<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Activate Your Account</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playpen+Sans:wght@100..800&family=Shantell+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,200..900;1,200..900&display=swap">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      img {
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100px;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(96, 158, 172) 0%, rgb(238, 228, 233) 100%);   
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .activation-code {
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 40px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: center; 
        letter-spacing: 15px;  
        color: #ba3d4f;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Activate Your Account</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p><strong>Hi {{fullName}},</strong></p>
        <p>
          Thank you for signing up with Stampted! To activate your account,
          please use the following 6-digit activation code:
        </p>
        <div class="activation-code">{{activationCode}}</div>
        <p>
          Enter this code in the activation form to complete the process. If you did not sign up for this account, you can safely ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Copyright 2024 Stampted. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
